    • load

      public static void load(String s, String n)
      load required clip into clips map.
      Parameters:
      s - s represent ResourceAsStream path/audio file name.
      n - n represent ResourceAsStream key in clips. call example : JukeBox.load("/SFX/playerlands.mp3", "playerlands");
